dataIdInfo.idPurp: The City of Ottawa - Park Inventory Geodatabase contains both spatial feature classes and non-spatial tables for all items found within City of Ottawa parks. The original inventory was collected in 2002, in the field, using IPAQs connected to Trimble Pathfinder Pocket GPS units. Data collection forms were customized for ESRI's ArcPAD GIS software to maintain data accuracy and completeness. The inventory has been maintained using a combination of field data collection and desktop updates from as-built plans, aerial photography, and city staff.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Feature class containing polygons for City of Ottawa parks.Updated as required.

Note: Use the PARK_ID field in this feature class to join the park name and address informationto other PR_*** feature classes.
